==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: The person is as tall as a horse is large.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén gāo mă dà

===Adjective===
'''[[人]][[高]][[马]][[大]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (of a person) unusually tall

===Alternate forms===
[[人]][[高]][[馬]][[大]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

